::Enertron::
       He hauls himself out of the base barely alive due to previous injuries 
that were never cared for.  He continues away from the base only to be sucked 
in by a passing micro-blackhole. (No, I didn't just make that up.)  The 
resulting damage to the surrounding environment was minor although there is 
now a nice path to the Predacon base which was somehow miraculously missed by 
the afore mentioned micro-blackhole.

--part1_8f.24953abf.2af897b6_boundary
